AttritionForecast: Analysis and Prediction

This project focuses on understanding and predicting employee attrition using HR data. It includes Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA), Business Intelligence dashboards, and Machine Learning models to help HR teams identify which employees are at risk of leaving and the key factors contributing to turnover.

Project Overview:

Employee attrition causes serious problems for organizations including loss of talent, higher hiring costs, reduced productivity, and workload pressure on remaining employees. This project answers the following questions:

Why are employees leaving?
Which employees are most likely to leave?
What factors are influencing attrition?
How can HR take proactive steps to reduce attrition?

This is an end-to-end HR analytics project covering EDA, BI visualization, and predictive modeling.

